&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chennai.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chennai&lt;/strong&gt; is the &lt;strong&gt;capital city of Tamil Nadu state&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Detroit is a city in Michigan&lt;/strong&gt; that is&lt;strong&gt; best known &lt;/strong&gt;as the &lt;strong&gt;birthplace of the modern automobile.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chennai &lt;/strong&gt;was&lt;strong&gt; previously called Madras&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Madras &lt;/strong&gt;became &lt;strong&gt;Chennai &lt;/strong&gt;in &lt;strong&gt;1996&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chennai &lt;/strong&gt;is nicknamed the &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Detroit of Asia&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;due to the presence of&lt;/em&gt; &lt;strong&gt;major automobile manufacturing units&lt;/strong&gt; and other industries around the city.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;More than one-third of India&amp;#39;s automobile industry is based in Chennai.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/important-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Important Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chennai is the oldest municipal corporation in India&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Indian Maritime University is situated in Chennai.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India&amp;#39;s first cyber post office was established in Chennai.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India&amp;#39;s first agricultural bank was established in Chennai.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The headquarters of the Southern Railway is in Chennai.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The famous Marina beach is in Chennai.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

